title: Videohive - After Effects Project Files - Butterfly Logo Reveal
description:
Follow a butterfly on a journey. It will land on the left side of your logo/message. This project could have many applications. A beautiful logo reveal, wedding intro, Nature message.

Technical:

The butterfly can land on your logo!
(For best results it can land on the left side of your logo)

Pre-Rendered footage

You can re-size and move your logo to position it behind the grass.

If you have a logo that is taller than it is broad, you can actually move the whole picture down, the underlying resolution is 1920Ãƒâ€”1480!

Make your custom wings in Photoshop and replace them!

Position and rotate the butterfly how you want it on the left side of the logo.
